    {
        "content": "<p>I just followed Axler's proof, which is via induction on the number of dimensions. And yes, there are still many important results missing <span aria-label=\"grinning\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f600\" role=\"img\" title=\"grinning\">:grinning:</span> . I haven't even defined the minimal polynomial yet. I'll keep your suggestion in mind and explore whether your approach is simpler to formalize.</p>",
