        "timestamp": 1600100313
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"112680\">Johan Commelin</span> <a href=\"#narrow/stream/144837-PR-reviews/topic/.234111/near/210028627\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Wait, I mean <code>minpoly</code> for lintrafos should make sense out of the box, right?</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Just need to show that linear transformations on finite-dimensional vector spaces are integral</p>",
